---
// ProGPT Landing Page
// Help brands rank inside ChatGPT & AI search results
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>ProGPT - Rank inside ChatGPT & AI Search</title>
	<style>
		* {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}

		body {
			font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #0a0a0a;
			color: #ffffff;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		/* Hero Section */
		.hero-section {
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
			padding: 100px 20px;
			text-align: center;
			min-height: 100vh;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 4rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #b0b0b0 100%);
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-clip: text;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			color: #a0a0a0;
			margin-bottom: 40px;
			max-width: 600px;
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}

		.cta-button {
			display: inline-block;
			background-color: #2563eb;
			color: #ffffff;
			padding: 16px 40px;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 8px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 600;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
			margin: 10px;
		}

		.cta-button:hover {
			background-color: #1d4ed8;
			transform: translateY(-2px);
			box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
		}

		/* How It Works Section */
		.how-it-works {
			background-color: #111111;
			padding: 80px 20px;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin-bottom: 50px;
			text-align: center;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		.steps-container {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 40px;
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.step {
			background-color: #1a1a1a;
			padding: 40px;
			border-radius: 12px;
			border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.step:hover {
			border-color: #2563eb;
			box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
		}

		.step-number {
			display: inline-block;
			width: 50px;
			height: 50px;
			background-color: #2563eb;
			color: #ffffff;
			border-radius: 50%;
			text-align: center;
			line-height: 50px;
			font-weight: 700;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.step-title {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-bottom: 15px;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		.step-description {
			color: #a0a0a0;
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		/* Why AI Search Matters */
		.why-ai-search {
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
			padding: 80px 20px;
		}

		.why-content {
			max-width: 900px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.benefits-list {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
			gap: 30px;
			margin-top: 40px;
		}

		.benefit {
			background-color: #1a1a1a;
			padding: 30px;
			border-radius: 12px;
			border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
		}

		.benefit-title {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		.benefit-text {
			color: #a0a0a0;
			font-size: 0.95rem;
		}

		/* CTA Section */
		.cta-section {
			background-color: #0a0a0a;
			padding: 80px 20px;
			text-align: center;
			border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
		}

		.cta-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin-bottom: 15px;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		.cta-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			color: #a0a0a0;
			margin-bottom: 40px;
			max-width: 600px;
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}

		.button-group {
			display: flex;
			gap: 15px;
			justify-content: center;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.cta-button-secondary {
			display: inline-block;
			background-color: transparent;
			color: #2563eb;
			padding: 16px 40px;
			border: 2px solid #2563eb;
			border-radius: 8px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 600;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.cta-button-secondary:hover {
			background-color: #2563eb;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		/* Footer */
		footer {
			background-color: #0a0a0a;
			border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
			padding: 30px 20px;
			text-align: center;
			color: #6a6a6a;
		}

		/* Responsive Design */
		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.hero-title {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
			}

			.hero-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}

			.section-title {
				font-size: 2rem;
			}

			.cta-title {
				font-size: 1.8rem;
			}

			.steps-container {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}

			.button-group {
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
			}

			.cta-button,
			.cta-button-secondary {
				width: 100%;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 480px) {
			.hero-section {
				padding: 50px 15px;
				min-height: auto;
			}

			.hero-title {
				font-size: 1.8rem;
			}

			.hero-subtitle {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.section-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}

			.cta-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}

			.step {
				padding: 25px;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero-section">
		<h1 class="hero-title">Rank inside ChatGPT & AI search</h1>
		<p class="hero-subtitle">We help brands appear inside AI-generated answers using AEO/GEO systems</p>
		<a href="#cta" class="cta-button">Get your brand ranked</a>
	</section>

	<!-- How It Works Section -->
	<section class="how-it-works">
		<h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
		<div class="steps-container">
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">1</div>
				<h3 class="step-title">Analyze Your Brand</h3>
				<p class="step-description">We audit your brand presence and identify optimisation opportunities for AI search engines and ChatGPT rankings.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">2</div>
				<h3 class="step-title">Optimize for AEO/GEO</h3>
				<p class="step-description">Our team implements AI Engine Optimisation (AEO) and Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO) strategies tailored to your brand.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">3</div>
				<h3 class="step-title">Monitor & Scale</h3>
				<p class="step-description">Track your rankings inside ChatGPT and other AI search results with real-time analytics and continuous optimisation.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why AI Search Matters -->
	<section class="why-ai-search">
		<div class="why-content">
			<h2 class="section-title">Why AI Search Matters</h2>
			<p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 40px;">AI-powered search is reshaping how consumers discover information. Being featured in ChatGPT and other AI models means unprecedented visibility and credibility for your brand.</p>
			<div class="benefits-list">
				<div class="benefit">
					<h3 class="benefit-title">✨ Higher Visibility</h3>
					<p class="benefit-text">Get featured directly in ChatGPT responses and AI search results, reaching millions of daily users.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit">
					<h3 class="benefit-title">🎯 Targeted Reach</h3>
					<p class="benefit-text">Appear when your ideal customers are asking AI models relevant questions about your industry.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit">
					<h3 class="benefit-title">📈 Authority & Trust</h3>
					<p class="benefit-text">AI mentions build credibility and authority faster than traditional SEO, establishing your brand as an industry leader.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="benefit">
					<h3 class="benefit-title">🚀 First-Mover Advantage</h3>
					<p class="benefit-text">Most brands haven't optimised for AI search yet. Claim your spot before competitors do.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="cta-section" id="cta">
		<h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Dominate AI Search?</h2>
		<p class="cta-subtitle">Join forward-thinking brands that are already ranking inside ChatGPT and AI search results.</p>
		<div class="button-group">
			<a href="#" class="cta-button">Get your brand ranked</a>
			<a href="#" class="cta-button-secondary">Learn more</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer>
		<p>&copy; 2026 ProGPT. All rights reserved. | Helping brands win in the age of AI.</p>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>
